        h2(class="modal-title").text-lg-center.text-uppercase.text-md-center.text-xs-center.line-height-1.dosis.m-t-1 COMPLETE THE FOLLOWING TO PUBLISH YOUR COMPANY

      .modal-body.m-b-2
        .form-section
